	<td>
		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Weeping Wand</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><a href="mailto:wendigo@virginia.edu">Plutarch Chath'luthin DeVir</a> | 
                        12/21/1999 8:32:20 AM</b></font></p>
			
			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">If you talk to Gardem he will say I need a silver wand from a silvered guard in cazic, a bloodback wand from the rathe mountains, twice woven silk from a faerie guard in the faydark and a sceptre of tears from the tomb in mistmoore&quot;  I've only done the sceptre so far and thats done by taking a flower from on top of the coffin (spawns every 5 mins or so) and giving it to the named shadowman (ssynthi, who also drops robe of the keeper when killed) directly behind the tomb.  he will give you &quot;a sceptre&quot; which is the sceptre of tears.  Have yet to complete other portions of quest.<BR>
The wand is a 1h blunt 5dam 25 delay 3ac 3int no drop wiz only weapon.
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
			</p>
	</td>
		<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
		
